OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1771949050
OL,3,CSouthport attack survivor launches
OL,4,Canti-knife crime fundraiser
OL,6,FA yoga teacher who survived the
OL,7,FSouthport attack has stepped up her
OL,8,Fcampaign to encourage the introduction
OL,9,Fof round-ended knives.
OL,11,FLeanne Lucas began her "Let's Be
OL,12,FBlunt" campaign after the July 2024
OL,13,Fattack in Merseyside in which Elsie
OL,14,FDot Stancombe, seven, Bebe King, six,
OL,15,Fand Alice da Silva Aguiar, nine, were
OL,16,Fmurdered.
OL,18,FEight children and two adults were
OL,19,Falso left injured when a 17-year-old
OL,20,Flaunched the knife attack on a Taylor
OL,21,FSwift-themed dance class.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
