FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1771949050
OL,3,CSouthport attack survivor launches
OL,4,Canti-knife crime fundraiser
OL,6,FSince the attack, Leanne Lucas has
OL,7,Fbeen calling for knife manufacturers
OL,8,Fand the public to stop using pointed-
OL,9,Ftip knives and instead opt for ones
OL,10,Fwith blunt ends.
OL,12,FThe yoga instructor and primary school
OL,13,Fteacher has now launched a community
OL,14,Finterest company (CIC) - a hybrid
OL,15,Fbetween a charity and business - to
OL,16,Fprovide prevention-led training to
OL,17,Fadults working with children in the
OL,18,Fpublic sector.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1771949050
OL,3,CSouthport attack survivor launches
OL,4,Canti-knife crime fundraiser
OL,6,FShe said: "We are already seeing real
OL,7,Fprogress. As demand increases, so does
OL,8,Fthe responsibility to deliver this
OL,9,Fwork well ` through training, policy
OL,10,Fengagement and practical resources."
OL,12,FLeanne was stabbed five times while
OL,13,Ftrying to save the 25 young girls, and
OL,14,Ffears another tragedy will happen if
OL,15,Fmore is not done to tackle knife crime.
OL,17,FIn a statement to the Southport
OL,18,Finquiry, she said she had met all the
OL,19,Fguidelines required when organising
OL,20,Fthe workshop.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
