OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1771949050
OL,3,CSouthport attack survivor launches
OL,4,Canti-knife crime fundraiser
OL,6,FShe said: "This was all irrelevant
OL,7,Fwhen faced with an unforeseen life or
OL,8,Fdeath situation, a situation that
OL,9,Fshould have been under control and
OL,10,Fprevented by multiple organisations
OL,11,Fand services that keep the general
OL,12,Fpublic safe.
OL,14,F"Those organisations and services have
OL,15,Flet me down."
OL,17,FShe is now asking members of the
OL,18,Fpublic to support the campaign and
OL,19,Fdonate to the CIC.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
