FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1771949050
OL,3,CSouthport attack survivor launches
OL,4,Canti-knife crime fundraiser
OL,6,FShe said: "What started as one voice
OL,7,Fspeaking up is now a registered
OL,8,FCommunity Interest Company working
OL,9,Fnationally to reduce knife harm
OL,10,Fthrough prevention-led action.
OL,12,F"As a CIC, we rely on community
OL,13,Fbacking to sustain and grow this work.
OL,15,F"If you believe harm should be
OL,16,Fprevented before it happens. If you
OL,17,Fbelieve adults need equipping as much
OL,18,Fas young people.
OL,20,F"If you believe prevention deserves
OL,21,Finvestment.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUwD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1771949050
OL,3,CSouthport attack survivor launches
OL,4,Canti-knife crime fundraiser
OL,6,F"Even small contributions help us
OL,7,Fcontinue this work and expand it into
OL,8,Fmore communities.
OL,10,F"Prevention rarely makes headlines.
OL,11,FBut it quietly changes futures."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@`O]
